  "title": "PUBLIC AREA ATTENDANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Responsible for cleanliness of public area</li><li>Sweep, scrubs and mop floors</li><li>Conduct frequent checks of all restrooms and clean them, replenishing amenities as required</li><li>Vacuum carpet, hard floors</li><li>Upholstery using appropriate machine and mechanical attachments</li><li>Ensuring economical use while replenishing supplies into restrooms</li><li>Carry out correct procedure for rubbish disposal</li><li>Reports all defects and update superior</li><li>Responsible for correct care and maintenance of all machinery and tools used.</li></ul>",
